title: Print, "Seesaw - Gloucester, Massachusetts, from Harper's Weekly, September 12, 1874, p. 757.", September 12, 1874
medium: Wood engraving in black ink on newsprint paper.
signed: Signed on block, lower right corner: WH
description: Horizontal group of children at the shore's edge:  three girls are seated in the foreground; beyond them is a seesaw with six boys; and sailboats are in background at right.
